      },
      {
        "id": "insc-20",
        "text": "Quinn and Ashley.",
        "font": {
          "family": "Great Vibes",
          "size_px": 13
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 88,
          "y_px": -71
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-29",
        "text": "We lived with the specter of death for such a long time,",
        "font": {
          "family": "Great Vibes",
          "size_px": 12
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 76,
          "y_px": -7
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-23",
        "text": "since you left my side.",
        "font": {
          "family": "Great Vibes",
          "size_px": 14
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 90,
          "y_px": -28
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-21",
        "text": "\"The days are so long, and the nights are longer,",
        "font": {
          "family": "Great Vibes",
          "size_px": 13
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 84,
          "y_px": -46
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-25",
        "text": "and you confounded death, (and doctors) with your strength & spirit.",
        "font": {
          "family": "Great Vibes",
          "size_px": 13
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 73,
          "y_px": 11
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-16",
        "text": "Loving Wife of Tom; Mother of Tracey, Michelle, Amy",
        "font": {
          "family": "Great Vibes",
          "size_px": 12
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 89,
          "y_px": -106
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-26",
        "text": "But now your race is run, and ours has just begun.",
        "font": {
          "family": "Great Vibes",
          "size_px": 13
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 68,
          "y_px": 31
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-30",
        "text": "She radiated Love & Friendship",
        "font": {
          "family": "Great Vibes",
          "size_px": 17
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 47,
          "y_px": 165
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-32",
        "text": "Until we meet again.",
        "font": {
          "family": "Great Vibes",
          "size_px": 17
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 54,
          "y_px": 188
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-18",
        "text": "and Kristy; Grandmother of Ava, Ashlyn, Aubrey, Aiden,",
        "font": {
          "family": "Great Vibes",
          "size_px": 12
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 86,
          "y_px": -88
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-35",
        "text": "but I wish I had loved you more.",
        "font": {
          "family": "Great Vibes",
          "size_px": 13
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 77,
          "y_px": 68
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-34",
        "text": "There was nothing left unsaid between us, we loved deeply,",
        "font": {
          "family": "Great Vibes",
          "size_px": 13
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 64,
          "y_px": 49
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-36",
        "text": "I wish so much to be with you, but you told me I had to stay behind",
        "font": {
          "family": "Great Vibes",
          "size_px": 14
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 39,
          "y_px": 88
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-37",
        "text": "and live my life.  I know time will help, but the huge hole in my heart",
        "font": {
          "family": "Great Vibes",
          "size_px": 13
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 40,
          "y_px": 105
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-38",
        "text": "can only ever partly heal.  We all have such wonderful memories ,",
        "font": {
          "family": "Great Vibes",
          "size_px": 13
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 41,
          "y_px": 123
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-39",
        "text": "to give us strength and to keep your spirit alive.     Tom\"",
        "font": {
